      "parameters": {
        "content": "### Route by Event Kind\n\nRoutes each item to one of 3 lanes: created, updated + fallback.\n\nPorts: ①→ Handle 'created' → Airtable · ②→ Handle 'updated' → Forward API · ③→ Log Unrecognized Kind",
