    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "### Handle 'created' → Airtable\n\nairtable — `upsert` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Consolidate Handling · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Airtable PAT",
        "width": 280,
